languages.text: "На этом мы простимся, чемпион. Я затаюсь в катакомбах Ефрата, чтобы наши враги думали, что я пал от твоей руки. Но я появляюсь вновь. Скоро. Очень скоро".
"We shall part ways for now, champion. I will lie low in the dungeons of Eufrates so that our enemies think I fell by your hand. But I shall resurface. Soon. Very soon."

languages.text: “我们暂且分道扬镳吧，勇士。我会躲在欧夫拉茨的地下区域，让我们的敌人误以为我已经死在了你手里。不过，我很快就会再次现身，很快。”
languages.original_text: "We shall part ways for now, champion. I will lie low in the dungeons of Eufrates so that our enemies think I fell by your hand. But I shall resurface. Soon. Very soon."

languages.text: "Unsere Wege trennen sich vorerst, Champion. Ich werde mich in den Verliesen von Eufrates verstecken, auf dass unsere Feinde glauben, ich sei durch Eure Hand gefallen. Doch ich werde wieder hervorkommen. Bald. Sehr bald."
languages.original_text: "We shall part ways for now, champion. I will lie low in the dungeons of Eufrates so that our enemies think I fell by your hand. But I shall resurface. Soon. Very soon."

traits.locale_text: "Unsere Wege trennen sich vorerst, Champion. Ich werde mich in den Verliesen von Eufrates verstecken, auf dass unsere Feinde glauben, ich sei durch Eure Hand gefallen. Doch ich werde wieder hervorkommen. Bald. Sehr bald."

languages.text: «Por ahora nuestros caminos se separan, adalid. Me ocultaré en las mazmorras de Eufrates para que nuestros enemigos crean que sucumbí por tu mano. Pero resurgiré. Pronto. Muy pronto».
languages.original_text: "We shall part ways for now, champion. I will lie low in the dungeons of Eufrates so that our enemies think I fell by your hand. But I shall resurface. Soon. Very soon."

traits.locale_text: «Por ahora nuestros caminos se separan, adalid. Me ocultaré en las mazmorras de Eufrates para que nuestros enemigos crean que sucumbí por tu mano. Pero resurgiré. Pronto. Muy pronto».

languages.text: « Pour le moment, {mf|champion|championne}, il nous faut nous séparer. Je me terrerai dans les cachots d'Euphrate et ainsi, nos ennemis croiront que vous m'avez terrassé. Mais je reviendrai. Bientôt, très bientôt. »
languages.original_text: "We shall part ways for now, champion. I will lie low in the dungeons of Eufrates so that our enemies think I fell by your hand. But I shall resurface. Soon. Very soon."

languages.text: 「王者よ、今は別れよう。私はユーフラテスの地下牢に身を潜め、敵に私がお前にやられたと思わせる。だが、またすぐ姿を現す。すぐに。本当にすぐにだ」
languages.original_text: "We shall part ways for now, champion. I will lie low in the dungeons of Eufrates so that our enemies think I fell by your hand. But I shall resurface. Soon. Very soon."

traits.locale_text: 「王者よ、今は別れよう。私はユーフラテスの地下牢に身を潜め、敵に私がお前にやられたと思わせる。だが、またすぐ姿を現す。すぐに。本当にすぐにだ」

languages.text: "Şimdilik yolumuz burada ayrılıyor müdafi. Eufrates'in zindanlarında göze batmadan varlığımı sürdüreceğim, böylece düşmanlarımız beni katlettiğini sanacak. Ancak yeniden gün yüzüne çıkacağım. Çok yakında. Hem de çok."
languages.original_text: "We shall part ways for now, champion. I will lie low in the dungeons of Eufrates so that our enemies think I fell by your hand. But I shall resurface. Soon. Very soon."
